Subject: Migrating to new network
Description: After moving the server to a new location and different subnet, and successfully assigned a static IP address in the new subnet. The server is not responding to ping or http or https.
What_We_Know__c: the customer cannot access the new appliance.
Next_Steps__c: waiting for the customer to provide more details
Solution_Comment__c: it was a case of slow downloads and upgrade process.
